'''快速射电暴'''（{{lang-en|Fast radio burst}}，缩写为{{lang|en|'''FRB'''}}）是一种[[宇宙学|宇宙学]]起源的[[高能天体物理|高能天体物理]]现象，呈現瞬態[[電波|電波]]脈衝，僅維持數[[毫秒|毫秒]]的爆發。辐射流量密度一般在<math>50\,\mathrm{mJy}</math>－<math>100\,\mathrm{Jy}</math>之间<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Fast radio bursts|url=http://link.springer.com/10.1007/s00159-019-0116-6|last=Petroff|first=E.|last2=Hessels|first2=J. W. T.|date=2019-12|journal=The Astronomy and Astrophysics Review|issue=1|doi=10.1007/s00159-019-0116-6|volume=27|pages=4|language=en|arxiv=1904.07947|bibcode=2019A&ARv..27....4P|issn=0935-4956|last3=Lorimer|first3=D. R.|s2cid=174799415}}</ref>。电波穿越[[電漿|電漿]]过程中发生色散，造成脉冲高频成分和低频成分之间有時間延遲<math>\Delta t</math>，它與[[色散_(光學)#脈衝星計時|頻散量]]<math>\mathrm{DM}</math>相關。快速電波爆發的色散量远超出银河系的色散量，表明其具有[[銀河系|銀河系]]外的起源<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Dense magnetized plasma associated with a fast radio burst|url=http://www.nature.com/articles/nature15769|last=Masui|first=Kiyoshi|last2=Lin|first2=Hsiu-Hsien|date=2015-12|journal=Nature|issue=7583|doi=10.1038/nature15769|volume=528|pages=523–525|language=en|issn=0028-0836|pmid=26633633|last3=Sievers|first3=Jonathan|last4=Anderson|first4=Christopher J.|last5=Chang|first5=Tzu-Ching|last6=Chen|first6=Xuelei|last7=Ganguly|first7=Apratim|last8=Jarvis|first8=Miranda|last9=Kuo|first9=Cheng-Yu|access-date=2021-10-18|archive-date=2022-04-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220412030530/https://www.nature.com/articles/nature15769}}</ref><ref name="lorimer2007">{{Cite journal|title=A Bright Millisecond Radio Burst of Extragalactic Origin|url=https://www.science.org/doi/10.1126/science.1147532|last=Lorimer|first=D. R.|last2=Bailes|first2=M.|date=2007-11-02|journal=Science|issue=5851|doi=10.1126/science.1147532|volume=318|pages=777–780|language=en|bibcode=2007Sci...318..777L|issn=0036-8075|last3=McLaughlin|first3=M. A.|last4=Narkevic|first4=D. J.|last5=Crawford|first5=F.|access-date=2021-10-18|archive-date=2022-05-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220520134638/https://www.science.org/doi/10.1126/science.1147532}}</ref>。

== 命名方式 ==
快速電波爆發的名字是依據錄得訊號的時間日期，以"YYMMDD"的排序命名。例如，第一個被發現的FRB是FRB 010621；2011年6月26日的FRB就稱為FRB 110626<ref name="thornton2013">{{Cite journal|title=A Population of Fast Radio Bursts at Cosmological Distances|url=https://www.science.org/doi/10.1126/science.1236789|last=Thornton|first=D.|last2=Stappers|first2=B.|date=2013-07-05|journal=Science|issue=6141|doi=10.1126/science.1236789|volume=341|pages=53–56|language=en|issn=0036-8075|pmid=23828936|last3=Bailes|first3=M.|last4=Barsdell|first4=B.|last5=Bates|first5=S.|last6=Bhat|first6=N. D. R.|last7=Burgay|first7=M.|last8=Burke-Spolaor|first8=S.|last9=Champion|first9=D. J.|access-date=2021-10-18|archive-date=2022-05-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220502140322/https://www.science.org/doi/10.1126/science.1236789}}</ref>。

== 观测历史 ==
=== 洛里默爆發 ===
2007年，[[邓肯·洛里默|邓肯·洛里默]]等人在澳大利亞帕克斯電波天文台2001年的檔案資料裡發現了洛里默爆發（FRB 010724）<ref name="McKee 20072">{{cite news|last=McKee|first=Maggie|url=https://www.newscientist.com/article/dn12699-extragalactic-radio-burst-puzzles-astronomers/|title=Extragalactic radio burst puzzles astronomers|work=New Scientist|date=27 September 2007|accessdate=2015-09-18|archive-date=2021-02-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210223215308/https://www.newscientist.com/article/dn12699-extragalactic-radio-burst-puzzles-astronomers/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。對資料分析發現在2001年7月24日發生了一個30[[揚斯基|央斯基]]的[[色散#在脈衝時計|色散爆發]]<ref name="lorimer20072">{{Cite journal|title=A Bright Millisecond Radio Burst of Extragalactic Origin|url=https://www.science.org/doi/10.1126/science.1147532|last=Lorimer|first=D. R.|last2=Bailes|first2=M.|date=2007-11-02|journal=Science|issue=5851|doi=10.1126/science.1147532|volume=318|pages=777–780|language=en|bibcode=2007Sci...318..777L|issn=0036-8075|last3=McLaughlin|first3=M. A.|last4=Narkevic|first4=D. J.|last5=Crawford|first5=F.|access-date=2021-10-18|archive-date=2022-05-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220520134638/https://www.science.org/doi/10.1126/science.1147532}}</ref>，持續時間短於5毫秒，位置距離[[小麥哲倫星系|小麥哲倫星系]]3°。這個爆發的屬性報告顯示與[[銀河系|銀河系]]和小麥哲倫星系都沒有物理上的關聯性，這就是現今所知的洛里默爆發<ref>{{cite journal|title=No flash in the pan|last=Chiao|first=May|date=2013|journal=Nature Physics|issue=8|doi=10.1038/nphys2724|volume=9|pages=454–454|bibcode=2013NatPh...9..454C}}</ref>。發現者以現存的自由電子模型在宇宙中的含量爭論這個爆發的距離小於10億[[秒差距|秒差距]]。在追加的90小時觀測時間內沒有進一步的爆發事實顯示這是一次奇異的事件，可能是一次超新星爆炸或相對論性的事件<ref name="lorimer20072" />。類似事件的发生率可能为每天數百次<ref name="Lorimer2007B2">{{cite web|title=A bright millisecond radio burst of extragalactic origin|url=http://www.atnf.csiro.au/news/newsletter/oct07/MSburst.htm|accessdate=2010-06-23|author=Duncan Lorimer (West Virginia University, USA)|date=October 2007|publisher=Australia Telescope National Facility|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201116080212/https://www.atnf.csiro.au/news/newsletter/oct07/MSburst.htm|archive-date=2020-11-16|dead-url=no|display-authors=4|author2=Matthew Bailes (Swinburne University)|author3=Maura McLaughlin (West Virginia University, USA)|author4=David Narkevic (West Virginia University, USA)|author5=Fronefield Crawford (Franklin & Marshall College, USA)|last-author-amp=yes}}</ref>。

=== 2010年 ===
在2010年，有16次類似的新脈衝報告：但顯然是起源於地球，且都是[[帕克斯天文台|帕克斯天文台]]檢測到的，被命名為{{link-en|佩利顿|Peryton (astronomy)}}（Peryton是指人造的[[鹿鹰兽|鹿鹰兽]]）<ref>{{Cite journal|title=RADIO BURSTS WITH EXTRAGALACTIC SPECTRAL CHARACTERISTICS SHOW TERRESTRIAL ORIGINS|url=https://iopscience.iop.org/article/10.1088/0004-637X/727/1/18|last=Burke-Spolaor|first=S.|last2=Bailes|first2=Matthew|date=2011-01-20|journal=The Astrophysical Journal|issue=1|doi=10.1088/0004-637X/727/1/18|volume=727|pages=18|arxiv=1009.5392v1|bibcode=2011ApJ...727...18B|issn=0004-637X|last3=Ekers|first3=Ronald|last4=Macquart|first4=Jean-Pierre|last5=Crawford III|first5=Fronefield|access-date=2021-10-18|archive-date=2021-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211019130902/https://iopscience.iop.org/article/10.1088/0004-637X/727/1/18}}</ref>。

=== 2012年 ===
==== FRB 121102 ====
2012年，[[阿雷西博天文台|阿雷西博電波望遠鏡]]在北半球的[[御夫座|御夫座]]方向上檢測到一次快速電波爆發（FRB 121102），由它的[[色散_(光學)#脈衝星計時|電漿頻散]]效應，證實是起源於銀河系之外。[[麥基爾大學|麥基爾大學]]的{{link-en|Victoria Kaspi|Victoria Kaspi}}估計在整個天空每天可以發生多達10,000次的快速電波爆發<ref>{{cite web|title=Radio-burst discovery deepens astrophysics mystery|url=http://www.mpifr-bonn.mpg.de/pressreleases/2014/8|access-date=2016-12-28|date=10 July 2014|publisher=Max Planck Institute|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201203051455/https://www.mpifr-bonn.mpg.de/pressreleases/2014/8|archive-date=2020-12-03|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 2013年 ===
2013年，有4次爆發事件支持了快速射电暴的河外起源<ref name="thornton2013" />。

=== 2014年 ===
FRB 140514被即時觀測到，並被發現有21%（±7%）的{{link-en|圆偏振|Circular polarization}}<ref name="RAS2015">{{cite web|title=Cosmic radio burst caught red-handed|url=https://www.ras.org.uk/news-and-press/2578-cosmic-radio-burst-caught-red-handed|access-date=2016-12-28|date=19 January 2015|website=Royal Astronomical Society|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150324212753/http://www.ras.org.uk/news-and-press/2578-cosmic-radio-burst-caught-red-handed|archive-date=2015-03-24|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

=== 2015年 ===
2015年1月19日，澳大利亞國家科學機構（[[聯邦科學與工業研究組織|聯邦科學與工業研究組織]]，CSIRO）的天文學家在帕克斯電波天文台首度直接觀測到FRB<ref name="RAS2015" />。

==== FRB 110523 ====
2015年，天文学家在[[綠堤望遠鏡|綠堤望遠鏡]]的檔案資料中被發現了FRB 110523<ref name="nature15769">{{Cite journal|title=Dense magnetized plasma associated with a fast radio burst|url=http://www.nature.com/articles/nature15769|last=Masui|first=Kiyoshi|last2=Lin|first2=Hsiu-Hsien|date=2015-12|journal=Nature|issue=7583|doi=10.1038/nature15769|volume=528|pages=523–525|language=en|arxiv=1512.00529|issn=0028-0836|pmid=26633633|last3=Sievers|first3=Jonathan|last4=Anderson|first4=Christopher J.|last5=Chang|first5=Tzu-Ching|last6=Chen|first6=Xuelei|last7=Ganguly|first7=Apratim|last8=Jarvis|first8=Miranda|last9=Kuo|first9=Cheng-Yu|access-date=2021-10-18|archive-date=2022-04-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220412030530/https://www.nature.com/articles/nature15769}}</ref>。它是第一個被檢測到{{link-en|線偏振|Linear polarization}}的FRB（然而，[[法拉第效應#星際物質造成的法拉第旋轉|法拉第旋轉]]的計算，允許檢測到的圓偏極化）。[[色散_(光學)|頻散延遲]]表明這次的爆發起源於外星系，距離可能遠達60億光年<ref name="p-FRB110523">{{cite web|title=Team finds detailed record of mysterious fast radio burst|url=http://phys.org/news/2015-12-team-mysterious-fast-radio.html|accessdate=2016-12-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190414125553/https://phys.org/news/2015-12-team-mysterious-fast-radio.html|archive-date=2019-04-14|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==== 乌龙事件 ====
Hippke et al. 分析了11个“快速射电暴”，发现它们的頻散量的中心值为 375，562，750，937，1125 cm<sup>−3</sup> pc，均接近187.5 cm<sup>−3</sup> pc的整数倍<ref name="hipp15">{{cite arXiv|last1=Hippke|first1=Michael|first2=Wilfried F.|last2=Domainko|first3=John G.|last3=Learned|title=Discrete steps in dispersion measures of Fast Radio Bursts|eprint=1503.05245|date=30 March 2015|class=astro-ph.HE}}</ref>。但是，後續的觀测否定了這種观点，它也被證實是[[微波爐|微波爐]]在加熱過程中，門被突然打開時由[[磁控管|磁控管]]產生的排放造成的烏龍事件<ref name="Petroff2015">{{Cite journal|title=Identifying the source of perytons at the Parkes radio telescope|url=https://academic.oup.com/mnras/article-lookup/doi/10.1093/mnras/stv1242|last=Petroff|first=E.|last2=Keane|first2=E. F.|date=2015-08-21|journal=Monthly Notices of the Royal Astronomical Society|issue=4|doi=10.1093/mnras/stv1242|volume=451|pages=3933–3940|language=en|arxiv=1504.02165|issn=0035-8711|last3=Barr|first3=E. D.|last4=Reynolds|first4=J. E.|last5=Sarkissian|first5=J.|last6=Edwards|first6=P. G.|last7=Stevens|first7=J.|last8=Brem|first8=C.|last9=Jameson|first9=A.|access-date=2021-10-18|archive-date=2021-11-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211110171735/https://academic.oup.com/mnras/article-lookup/doi/10.1093/mnras/stv1242}}</ref>。

==== FRB 150418 ====
2015年4月18日，帕克斯天文台檢測到FRB 150418，數小時內好幾架望遠鏡，包括[[澳大利亞望遠鏡緻密陣列|澳大利亞望遠鏡緻密陣列]]都捕捉到閃光的餘輝，並且經過6天才黯淡至看不見<ref name="galaxy">{{cite news|last=Webb|first=Jonathan|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/science-environment-35645370|title=Radio flash tracked to faraway galaxy|work=BBC News|date=24 February 2016|accessdate=2016-02-24|archive-date=2021-02-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210204024137/https://www.bbc.com/news/science-environment-35645370|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Keane 2016">{{cite journal|title=The host galaxy of a fast radio burst|last=Keane|first=E. F.|last2=Johnston|first2=S.|date=25 February 2016|journal=Nature|issue=7591|doi=10.1038/nature17140|volume=530|pages=453–461|arxiv=1602.07477|bibcode=2016Natur.530..453K|display-authors=etal}}</ref><ref name="Plait 2016">{{cite news|last=Plait|first=Phil|url=http://www.slate.com/blogs/bad_astronomy/2016/02/24/fast_radio_bursts_finally_identified_as_being_very_far_away.html|title=Astronomers Solve One Mystery of Fast Radio Bursts and Find Half the Missing Matter in the Universe|work=Bad Astronomy – Slate|date=24 February 2016|accessdate=2016-02-24|archive-date=2018-10-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181015144327/http://www.slate.com/blogs/bad_astronomy/2016/02/24/fast_radio_bursts_finally_identified_as_being_very_far_away.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[昴星團望遠鏡|昴星團望遠鏡]]被用於尋找它的宿主星系，並且用來確定它的[[紅移|紅移]]和隱含於爆炸的距離<ref name="New FRB">{{cite news|url=http://spaceref.com/astronomy/new-fast-radio-burst-discovery-finds-missing-matter-in-the-universe.html|title=New Fast Radio Burst Discovery Finds Missing Matter in the Universe|work=Subaru Telescope|publisher=Space Ref|date=24 February 2016|accessdate=2016-02-25}}</ref>。

然而，這次爆發的來源很快就引起了質疑<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=Cosmological Origin for FRB 150418? Not So Fast|url=http://newton.cx/~peter/wp/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/note-rev1.pdf|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160306074607/http://newton.cx/~peter/wp/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/note-rev1.pdf|archive-date=2016-03-06|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":1">{{Cite web|title=ATel #8752: Radio brightening of FRB 150418 host galaxy candidate|url=http://www.astronomerstelegram.org/?read=8752|access-date=2016-03-03|website=ATel|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190103100519/http://www.astronomerstelegram.org/?read=8752|archive-date=2019-01-03|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":2">{{Cite web|title=That Blast of Radio Waves Produced By Colliding Dead Stars? Not So Fast.|url=http://phenomena.nationalgeographic.com/2016/02/29/that-blast-of-radio-waves-produced-by-colliding-dead-stars-not-so-fast/|access-date=2016-03-03|last=says|first=Franko|website=Phenomena|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170912011209/http://phenomena.nationalgeographic.com/2016/02/29/that-blast-of-radio-waves-produced-by-colliding-dead-stars-not-so-fast/|archive-date=2017-09-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並且在2016年4月被確認為是起源於一個活躍星系核，是[[超大質量黑洞|超大質量黑洞]]雙極噴流向外排放的能量爆發<ref name="HSCFA 2016">{{cite news|url=http://spaceref.com/astronomy/fast-radio-burst-afterglow-was-actually-a-flickering-black-hole.html|title=Fast Radio Burst Afterglow Was Actually a Flickering Black Hole|work=Harvard-Smithsonian Center for Astrophysics (HSCFA)|publisher=SpaceRef|date=April 4, 2016|accessdate=2016-04-05}}</ref>。它還被指出為什麼餘輝永遠不會消失，意味著它與快速電波爆發毫無關聯<ref name="HSCFA 2016"/>。

2015年11月，加拿大[[麥基爾大學|麥基爾大學]]的天文學家保羅·朔爾茨在阿雷西博電波望遠鏡當年5月和6月的檔案資料中發現10個非週期性重複出現的快速電波脈衝<ref name="McGill">{{cite news|last=Chipello|first=Chris|url=https://www.mcgill.ca/newsroom/channels/news/mysterious-cosmic-radio-bursts-found-repeat-259440|title=Mysterious cosmic radio bursts found to repeat|work=McGill University News|date=2 March 2016|accessdate=2016-03-05|archive-date=2020-11-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201128053901/https://www.mcgill.ca/newsroom/channels/news/mysterious-cosmic-radio-bursts-found-repeat-259440|dead-url=no}}</ref>。這10次爆發的頻散值和在天空中的位置與2012年檢測到的FRB 121102一致<ref name="McGill" />。如同2012年的爆發，這10個有三次源自[[銀河系|銀河系]]的最大[[電漿|電漿]][[色散_(光學)#脈衝星計時|頻散值]]。研究小組認為，這一現象排除了可能只能出現一次，如同一個黑洞或兩顆中子星碰撞爆炸的自我毀滅等災難性的事件<ref name="Woo 2016">{{cite news|last=Woo|first=Marcus|url=http://www.bbc.com/earth/story/20160606-there-are-weird-bursts-of-energy-coming-from-deep-space|title=There a re weird bursts of energy coming from deep space|work=BBC News|date=7 June 2016|accessdate=2016-06-07|archive-date=2021-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210225162206/http://www.bbc.com/earth/story/20160606-there-are-weird-bursts-of-energy-coming-from-deep-space|dead-url=no}}</ref>。據科學家說，這一資料支持起源於年輕的自轉[[中子星|中子星]]（[[脈衝星|波煞]]）或高度磁化的中子星（[[磁星|磁星]]）<ref name="McGill" /><ref name="Woo 2016"/><ref name="Spitler">{{Cite journal|title=A repeating fast radio burst|url=http://www.nature.com/nature/journal/vaop/ncurrent/full/nature17168.html|last=Spitler|first=L. G.|last2=Scholz|first2=P.|date=2016-03-02|journal=Nature|doi=10.1038/nature17168|volume=advance online publication|pages=202–205|language=en|arxiv=1603.00581|bibcode=2016Natur.531..202S|issn=1476-4687|last3=Hessels|first3=J. W. T.|last4=Bogdanov|first4=S.|last5=Brazier|first5=A.|last6=Camilo|first6=F.|last7=Chatterjee|first7=S.|last8=Cordes|first8=J. M.|last9=Crawford|first9=F.|access-date=2016-12-28|archive-date=2020-03-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200330134706/http://www.nature.com/nature/articles|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="NalGeo">{{Cite web|title=Astronomers Discover a New Kind of Radio Blast From Space|url=http://news.nationalgeographic.com/2016/03/160302-fast-radio-burst-discovery-magnetar-repeated-waves/|access-date=2016-03-03|date=2 March 2016|last=Draka|first=Nadia|website=National Geographic News|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161217091538/http://news.nationalgeographic.com/2016/03/160302-fast-radio-burst-discovery-magnetar-repeated-waves/|archive-date=2016-12-17|dead-url=no}}</ref>，或是高度磁化的脈衝星穿越小行星帶<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Repeating Fast Radio Bursts from Highly Magnetized Pulsars Travelling through Asteroid Belts|url=http://arxiv.org/abs/1603.08207|last=G.|first=Dai, Z.|last2=S.|first2=Wang, J.|date=2016-03-27|journal=|last3=F.|first3=Wu, X.|last4=F.|first4=Huang, Y.|access-date=2016-12-28|archive-date=2021-01-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210101041108/https://arxiv.org/abs/1603.08207|dead-url=no}}</ref>，或是從白矮星聯星的洛希瓣間歇溢出<ref>{{Cite journal|title=A NEUTRON STAR–WHITE DWARF BINARY MODEL FOR REPEATING FAST RADIO BURST 121102|url=https://iopscience.iop.org/article/10.3847/2041-8205/823/2/L28|last=Gu|first=Wei-Min|last2=Dong|first2=Yi-Ze|date=2016-05-24|journal=The Astrophysical Journal|issue=2|doi=10.3847/2041-8205/823/2/L28|volume=823|pages=L28|issn=2041-8213|last3=Liu|first3=Tong|last4=Ma|first4=Renyi|last5=Wang|first5=Junfeng|access-date=2021-10-18|archive-date=2021-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211019130858/https://iopscience.iop.org/article/10.3847/2041-8205/823/2/L28}}</ref>。

