== 观测特征 ==
=== 色散量 ===
色散量（Dispersion measure，缩写为DM）是传播路径上自由电子柱密度<math>n_\mathrm{e}</math>的积分：
:<math>\mathrm{DM} = \int_0^d{n_e\;dl}</math>

其单位为<math>\rm{pc}/\rm{cm}^{-3}</math>。<ref>{{Cite book|title=Handbook of pulsar astronomy|url=https://www.worldcat.org/title/handbook-of-pulsar-astronomy/oclc/968450427|publisher=University Press|date=2012|location=Cambridge|isbn=978-0-521-53534-2|oclc=968450427|language=en|first=Duncan Ross, Kramer, Michael|last=Lorimer|access-date=2021-10-18|archive-date=2021-10-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211018070944/https://www.worldcat.org/title/handbook-of-pulsar-astronomy/oclc/968450427}}</ref>

对于某频率<math>\nu</math>的信号，其传播时间为：
:<math>t = k_\mathrm{DM} \cdot \left(\frac{\mathrm{DM}}{\nu^2}\right)</math>

其中色散常量<math>k_\mathrm{DM}</math>为
:<math> k_\mathrm{DM} = \frac{e^2}{2 \pi m_\mathrm{e}c} \simeq 4.149\, \mathrm{GHz}^2\,\mathrm{pc}^{-1}\,\mathrm{cm}^3\,\mathrm{ms}</math><ref>{{Cite book|url=https://www.worldcat.org/title/single-dish-radio-astronomy-techniques-and-applications-proceedings-of-the-naic-nrao-summer-school-held-at-national-astronomy-and-ionosphere-center-arecibo-observatory-arecibo-puerto-rico-usa-10-15-june-2001/oclc/51812223|publisher=Astronomical Society of the Pacific|date=2002|location=San Francisco, Calif.|isbn=978-1-58381-120-7|oclc=51812223|editor-first=Stanimirović, Snežana|editor-last=NAIC-NRAO School on Single Dish Radio Astronomy|title=Single-dish radio astronomy: techniques and applications : proceedings of the NAIC-NRAO summer school held at National Astronomy and Ionosphere Center, Arecibo Observatory, Arecibo, Puerto Rico, USA, 10-15 June 2001|pages=251-269|access-date=2021-10-18|archive-date=2021-10-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211018070955/https://www.worldcat.org/title/single-dish-radio-astronomy-techniques-and-applications-proceedings-of-the-naic-nrao-summer-school-held-at-national-astronomy-and-ionosphere-center-arecibo-observatory-arecibo-puerto-rico-usa-10-15-june-2001/oclc/51812223}}</ref>

则脉冲高频成分<math>\nu_\mathrm{hi}</math>和低频成分<math>\nu_\mathrm{lo}</math>之间的时间延迟<math>\Delta t</math>为
:<math>\Delta t = k_\mathrm{DM} \cdot \mathrm{DM} \cdot \left( \frac{1}{\nu_{\mathrm{lo}}^2} - \frac{1}{\nu_{\mathrm{hi}}^2} \right)</math>

